  "key": "B minor",
  "genre": [
    "Alternative",
    "Indie"
  ],
  "difficultyLevel": 4,
  "lyrics": "At night I've been sleeping too long Now I'm letting my mind turn on I can't get the rest I need to make myself feel better And I can't get the rest I need Dreams, if they fall you can see Dreams, are they really for a team? At night I keep chasing thoughts and worry about the life that I call this disaster Calm down, I don't know which way to grade me But it's probably only negative if I'm really being true I gotta know better than that If I'm gonna move past anything in this existence If I'm gonna be better than I can find resistance in the competition that we all go through I wanna find the gratitude, be there for you too and me, myself And maybe we can add more into our family, our life and be different and find ourselves Dreaming again, dreaming again About the things we wanted in the beginning When we took this drive down our little course At the sideways of normal baby we can still behave It doesn't have to be this do or die, yeah So we can dream again, dream again Fall asleep in comfort and hold each other tight As we dream again, dream again And I will be dreaming and dreaming and dreaming of different times Cause what dream is right for you is not right for me Is it different particles of family that make us stay here And emotionally entangled, the other one because we just don't want to Go one more day without that touch, without the love that makes me sore Come on, find that calming ground and close your eyes for more Baby we'll dream again, sing again Come on, dream my friend www.mooji.org",
  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 24.020000457763672,
      "text": "At night I've been sleeping too long Now I'm letting my mind turn on",
      "start": 0
    },
    {
      "end": 31.6200008392334,
      "text": "I can't get the rest I need to make myself feel better",
      "start": 24.020000457763672
    },
    {
      "end": 36.2400016784668,
      "text": "And I can't get the rest I need",
      "start": 31.68000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 44.02000045776367,
      "text": "Dreams, if they fall you can see",
      "start": 38.619998931884766
    },
    {
      "end": 51.099998474121094,
      "text": "Dreams, are they really for a team?",
      "start": 45.15999984741211
    },
    {
      "end": 59.84000015258789,
      "text": "At night I keep chasing thoughts and worry about the life that I call this disaster",
      "start": 52.099998474121094
    },
    {
      "end": 68.04000091552734,
      "text": "Calm down, I don't know which way to grade me",
      "start": 61.459999084472656
    },
    {
      "end": 72.87999725341797,
      "text": "But it's probably only negative if I'm really being true",
      "start": 68.04000091552734
    },
    {
      "end": 77.19999694824219,
      "text": "I gotta know better than that",
      "start": 73.62000274658203
    },
    {
      "end": 81,
      "text": "If I'm gonna move past anything in this existence",
      "start": 77.19999694824219
    },
    {
      "end": 88.33999633789062,
      "text": "If I'm gonna be better than I can find resistance in the competition that we all go through",
      "start": 81
    },
    {
      "end": 93.69999694824219,
      "text": "I wanna find the gratitude, be there for you too and me, myself",
      "start": 89.04000091552734
    },
    {
      "end": 101.13999938964844,
      "text": "And maybe we can add more into our family, our life and be different and find ourselves",
      "start": 93.69999694824219
    },
    {
      "end": 107.13999938964844,
      "text": "Dreaming again, dreaming again",
      "start": 101.13999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 111.22000122070312,
      "text": "About the things we wanted in the beginning",
      "start": 108.13999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 115.13999938964844,
      "text": "When we took this drive down our little course",
      "start": 111.22000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 120.87999725341797,
      "text": "At the sideways of normal baby we can still behave",
      "start": 116.13999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 127.54000091552734,
      "text": "It doesn't have to be this do or die, yeah",
      "start": 122.13999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 133.5399932861328,
      "text": "So we can dream again, dream again",
      "start": 127.54000091552734
    },
    {
      "end": 140.47999572753906,
      "text": "Fall asleep in comfort and hold each other tight",
      "start": 134.24000549316406
    },
    {
      "end": 145.5399932861328,
      "text": "As we dream again, dream again",
      "start": 140.47999572753906
    },
    {
      "end": 152.63999938964844,
      "text": "And I will be dreaming and dreaming and dreaming of different times",
      "start": 146.3800048828125
    },
    {
      "end": 157,
      "text": "Cause what dream is right for you is not right for me",
      "start": 153.4199981689453
    },
    {
      "end": 159.9600067138672,
      "text": "Is it different particles of family that make us stay here",
      "start": 157
    },
    {
      "end": 164.63999938964844,
      "text": "And emotionally entangled, the other one because we just don't want to",
      "start": 159.9600067138672
    },
    {
      "end": 172.77999877929688,
      "text": "Go one more day without that touch, without the love that makes me sore",
      "start": 165.8800048828125
    },
    {
      "end": 178.5800018310547,
      "text": "Come on, find that calming ground and close your eyes for more",
      "start": 173.16000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 185.05999755859375,
      "text": "Baby we'll dream again, sing again",
      "start": 178.5800018310547
    },
    {
      "end": 190,
      "text": "Come on, dream my friend",
      "start": 185.5800018310547
    },
    {
      "end": 216.47999572753906,
      "text": "www.mooji.org",
      "start": 215.0399932861328
    }
  ],
